    { point: "Final separation", text1Evidence: "How strange now it seems / With this distance between, / And that silence so when / You come next beside me", text2Evidence: "Let me come home", analysis: "Byron presents permanent separation; Armitage presents attempted reconciliation within ongoing conflict. Different endings." }
